00:24:41,424 --> 00:24:44,094
Oh, I knew that right away.

247
00:24:44,177 --> 00:24:46,471
Me too.

248
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:50,100
You and l-

249
00:24:50,141 --> 00:24:52,102
we're the same.

250
00:24:55,563 --> 00:24:57,482
We have personality!

251
00:25:00,110 --> 00:25:02,195
Is your personality chip
turned on?

252
00:25:03,571 --> 00:25:06,449
- Isn't yours?
- No.

253
00:25:07,700 --> 00:25:09,619
Sucks to be you!

254
00:25:09,702 --> 00:25:15,542
I think personality is
much more fun than intelligence,
don't you?

255
00:25:15,625 --> 00:25:18,962
- Baby, baby, sweet baby
- I think so.

256
00:25:20,422 --> 00:25:24,008
There's somethin'
that I've just got to say

257
00:25:24,092 --> 00:25:26,010
Can I help you?

258
00:25:26,094 --> 00:25:29,013
Your robot is just
a standard NDR, isn't she?

259
00:25:30,265 --> 00:25:32,475
Yeah, I'm afraid so.

260
00:25:32,559 --> 00:25:35,228
Why does she have
the ability to dance?

261
00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:37,230
'Cause l, uh-

262
00:25:37,272 --> 00:25:41,484
I put a modified skeletal chip
into her during a rebuild.

263
00:25:41,568 --> 00:25:44,487
- How were you able
to do that modification?
