could cut both ways.

444
00:42:26,489 --> 00:42:30,452
I don't think that any
existing prosthetic devices
or artificial organs...

445
00:42:30,535 --> 00:42:33,079
hold a candle
to what you've designed here.

446
00:42:33,163 --> 00:42:37,000
