in human beings as well.

447
00:42:37,041 --> 00:42:39,002
Exactly.

448
00:42:40,420 --> 00:42:42,338
Wow!

449
00:43:15,121 --> 00:43:18,541
- What a piece of fecal matter.
- Shit.

